posting_body: ['Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath', 'If you’ve been searching for a spacious apartment in the Katy ISD, look no further than Kenwood Club at the Park.', 'Located west of Houston in Katy, TX, our one, two, and three bedroom apartments for rent offer the ideal retreat.', 'Relax in the comfort of your oversized floor plan, complete with walk-in closets and a private patio, or take advantage of our many community amenities, including a refreshing swimming pool and fully equipped fitness center.', 'At Kenwood Club at the Park, the choice is yours.', 'Features:', 'Carpeting, Disability Access, Garden Tub, Refrigerator, Air Conditioning, Island Kitchen*, Cable Ready, Washer & Dryer Connections, Stove, Ceiling Fans, Oversized Closets, Built-In Bookshelves*, Vaulted Ceilings, Dishwasher, Private Patio or Balcony, Fireplace', '*In Select Homes', 'Community Amenities:', 'Door-to-Door Valet Trash Service – 5 Nights per Week**, Laundry Facility, Playground, Garage Parking Available, Swimming Pool, Modernized Online Move-In Experience, Fitness Center, High-Speed Internet Access in Common Areas, Recycling Program Available**, Bark Park for Your Furry Friends, 24-Hour Emergency Maintenance Available, Volleyball Court, Controlled-Access Community', '**', 'For those who apply', 'Pet Policy', 'Kenwood Club at the Park is happy to be a pet-friendly Katy apartment community.', 'We welcome both cats and dogs into our homes, and even provide a dog Bark Park so your pet is free to stretch their legs and socialize with others around the community.', 'Fees and restrictions apply.', 'Want more information?', 'Follow this link:', '<URL>', '3I29sHhT']
